==Etymology==
Modification of English [[-orama]], influenced by [[diarama]]
==English==
===Suffix===
'''-rama'''
# Alteration of [[-orama]] (q.v.), used in suffixing a word ending with an ''r'' or vowel sound, for example, 
#: ''camera'' to form ''camerarama'' or 
#: ''future'' to form (eliding the ''e'' and merging the two ''r''s into one) ''futurama'' 

==== Usage note ====
* The suffix is usually appended without hyphenation, or occasionally with hyphen intended to catch the eye.